{"tid":254044,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"當它來襲時　美國每年將有30萬司機失業 (05:09)","createTime":"2017-05-23T00:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T07:20:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00232978493b9a0129a89dd3b5284beb2c6b4742","tid":254044,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=nC8wVHy36zhM20HqL3oKBJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=285315d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】大行高盛報告預料，當自動車輛飽和度達到峰值時，美國司機可能會以每月25,000的速度失業，這意味每年將有30萬司機失業。<br />\n<br />\n不過該行認為，自駕汽車要全方面的影響社會還需要數十年的時間，但當它來襲時，美國卡車司機將大面積失業。<br />\n<br />\n然而，卡車司機的失業人數會遠遠高於公共汽車司機或出租車司機。事實上，2014年，美國有400萬個司機工作，其中310萬是卡車司機，高盛說，這一數字占到全美就業總人數的2%。<br />\n<br />\n該報告估計，2025至2030年，半自動和完全自動的汽車銷售量將占到汽車總銷售的20%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170523/20170523050901fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170523%2F20170523050901fi.html&d=nC8wVHy36zhM20HqL3oKBJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=684e5790\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170523/20170523050901fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5dd7e694a9c51afdfff847b1aab903973d08f8d","tid":254044,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:56:45.000Z","msg":"路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e73c4dbb39cc0ae08c26e48c0fe07eff9297d97","tid":254044,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>人會疲勞 疲勞就會專注力／集中力下降 自動就無呢個弱點"},{"pid":"d0eade6a4f78381ea558d0f4c3fb068322b236d2","tid":254044,"uid":82562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公路上面揾條線，淨係俾自動駕駛行，已經差好遠"},{"pid":"7795b068f97bee9c2abcc186509529689ce269e4","tid":254044,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>人會疲勞 疲勞就會專注力／集中力下降 自動就無呢個弱點</blockquote><br />\n自動駕駛反應力靠sensor<br />\n未必夠人快"},{"pid":"b1703ae92e6530c101cc6a623cf908bdaa46334e","tid":254044,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以下一步可能是全面自動化<br />\n理論上全部車都係電腦控制+網路連接<br />\n可以將 情況千變萬化 減到極低<br />\n<br />\n唔考慮安全等因素"},{"pid":"bce76962eb2c6986389a3bd228053c0f10ee0a9f","tid":254044,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以下一步可能是全面自動化<br />\n理論上全部車都係電腦控制+<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">網路連接</span></span><br />\n可以將 情況千變萬化 減到極低<br />\n<br />\n唔考慮安全等因素</blockquote><br />\n咁會唔會增加網絡惡意攻擊風險？"},{"pid":"21ee9503473581a66d3db5bf1a12e28e9f6c531a","tid":254044,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"仲有保險問題，出事邊個賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連上internet數據出錯而導致交通意外又點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 突然有野衝出馬路全自動反應夠唔夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a208793665ff3f2b82178725c4efa61a54fb6b","tid":254044,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>路面情況千變萬化，隨時有突發野，真係可以自動/半自動駕駛搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/